BA Basic fare includes:-

• Changes before/after at a charge
• Refunds not available
• Seating at a charge
• Hand Baggage 23kgs max (126LCM)
• Laptop or Handbag included
• Food and Bar service on-board

• Please note that if the flight is operated by another airline then the onboard product or service maybe different to that described above.
The fare to suit those travelling light

Enjoy your well cushioned and spacious economy seat with a full meal on medium & long flights or light snacks on short flights. Inflight entertainment programs put the choice in your hands.

Economy Extra fares include:

• Carry on Baggage 1 X 7KG 
• Checked bags for international flights 1 X 32KG
• Meals 
• Earn Miles 
• Choose your own seat 
• Refund permitted at a fee                             
• Changes permitted at a fee
• Please note that if the flight is operated by another airline then the onboard product or service maybe different to that described above.
Traveling with hand baggage only? This is the fare for you

Included

• Hand baggage : 1 item up to 7 kg*

Available for a fee
• Checked baggage
• Meal and beverages
• Seat selection in advance
• Business Lounge access
• Boarding pass at the airport

Not available
• Booking changes & Refund 
• Priority check-in & boarding 

*Embraer-145 hand baggage allowance: 5 kg
Traveling with hand baggage only? This is the fare for you

The best inflight entertainment, a selection of fine international cuisine, and warm Arabian hospitality. Welcome to Etihad Economy Class.

• Refunds not permitted**
• Changes not permitted**
• Checked baggage Included**
• Hand baggage x 1 bag up to 7kgs
• Seat assignment at a fee**
• 25% Etihad Guest miles
• Available Wi-Fi on board

**Please refer to fare rules for full terms and conditions
***Imagery provided from our A380 services only
• Please note that if the flight is operated by another airline then the onboard product or service maybe different to that described above.

KLM Economy Class includes: 

- Comfortable modern seating. 
- Complimentary meals and drinks on board. 
- Personal seat back entertainment system on board long haul flights. 
- WiFi available on all of our brand new Boeing 787 Dreamliners and on 1 of our Boeing 777-300 aircraft. 

If the flight is operated by another airline then the onboard product or service might be different.
The fare to suit those travelling light

With a spacious 34-inch pitch, Oman Air's Economy Class offers everything the modern traveller needs to stay connected, informed and entertained.

Saver Economy includes:

• Changes at a fee*
• Refunds at a fee*
• Checked baggage 2 bag x 15kg
• Hand baggage 1 bag x 7kg
• Standard seating complimentary
• Choice seating at a fee*
• Inflight dining
• Inflight Entertainment
• Wi-Fi available on selected aircraft for a fee
• Lounge services available in Muscat and Bangkok for a fee
• Earn 25% of flown miles as Sindbad miles
• Upgrade eligibility with Sindbad miles

*Please refer to fare rules for full conditions
• Please note that if the flight is operated by another airline then the onboard product or service maybe different to that described above.
Includes the option to refund against a fee
